<title>
<![CDATA[ Up to $65k/year | Senior Accountant | Charlotte, NC (Hybrid) ]]>
</title>
<url>
<![CDATA[ https://arraycorp.com/job/up-to-65k-year-senior-accountant-charlotte-nc-hybrid/?ad_id=78fb416f-cd24-de29-d011-3a155fde3d13&source=A2E8403E-F59F-4BA7-FF98-3A102FA6D2E5 ]]>
